    "description": {
      "value": "<h2>Too Hot To Touch</h2><p>The Shakuton Clan is a clan that hails proudly from the Land of Wind. This clan has an extreme affinity for Fire &amp; Wind Release able to create flames as hot as a small sun that can burn away all moisture on impact. This clan has a famed history in the Land of Wind, but after one of its famed members were killed in an ambush, they scattered joining other villages to avoid the potential of a clan massacre.</p><hr /><h3>Shakuton Traits</h3><p><strong>Recommended Ability Score Increase</strong>: +2 Int, +1 Wis</p><p><strong>Speed</strong>: Your base walking speed is 30 feet.</p><p><strong>Skill Proficiencies</strong>: Survival, Ninshou.</p><p><strong>Scorch Release</strong> <strong>Affinity</strong>: You begin with either Wind or Fire Release Affinity. (Pick one)</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
